        <h1>Travel Information Reminder for TfL services over the Festive Period</h1>
        <div class="content-page-press-release">
        22 December 2009
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="main-and-aside r">
    <div class="main" role="main">

    <div class="article-teaser">
        Londoners and visitors travelling in the Capital over this period are reminded to 'check before they travel' as there will be some changes to normal services.
        
    </div>



<div class="pull-quote">
